headline: DaVita (NYSE:DVA) Beats Expectations in Strong Q4 CY2025, Stock Soars
summary: Dialysis provider DaVita Inc. (NYSE:DVA) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 9.9% year on year to $3.62 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $3.40 per share was 6.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Elara Caring Secures New Strategic Investment from Ares and DaVita
summary: DALLAS, February 02, 2026--Elara Caring (Elara), a leading national provider of skilled home health, hospice, behavioral health, and personal care services, today announced that it has entered into an agreement for a strategic investment from Ares’ Private Equity Group (Ares) and DaVita.
